name: Experiment Or Die #89
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The 7th letter in The Cool Alphabet had me torn a bit because Mario really is synonymous with Nintendo, but I really wanted to feature them both so here we are. Some of my oldest gaming memories were spending hours trying to beat Mario 3 only to find out there are awesome shortcuts to cruise through that game. Many sleepless sleepover nights trying to discover all the secrets Mario had to offer. All hail the king. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
